This is example for how to create own library and publish local npm

reference site : https://jinalshah999.medium.com/how-to-build-and-publish-angular-library-a333d6ff12c0


ng new anuguarLibraryProject

ng generate library my-demo-lib


create you functions then

ng build my-demo-lib

open disc folder created compiled build files

open disc/your-library-name folder

npm pack

make a Pack (target) file with a name .tgz extenstion

publishing done you can import your project


how to import your own library to new project

ng new angularTry1

npm i .tgz file location




commend for create component specific project
ng g c CounterDemo --project my-demo-lib
